*Vidjela* sam ga kako se vraća kući. (I saw him coming back home.)

Bio je *vidjen* odmah nakon što je otišao. (He was seen right after he left.)

*Vidjeli* smo se nakon dugo vremena. (We saw each other after a long time.)

Ona je *vidjela* da je on lažirao. (She saw that he was lying.)

*Vidjela* je kako se njegova ljubav izmenila. (She saw how his love changed.)